food grade quality nsf   compound lead and cadmium free low temperature formula formulated compounds to retard mold and mildew growth walk in cooler gaskets and strip curtains are also available shipped typically  days from receipt of order about us acent technologies inc  n rainbow rd   las vegas nv    fax contact us july  m t w t f s s « feb              designed by the computer guys  powered by wordpress led lights  acent technologies home led lights grow lights night blinds product graphics gaskets strip curtains leasing utility rebates contact us about us return policy navigation menu home » led lights led lights   the emergence of leds as a useful alternative to incandescent lighting can be credited to new manufacturing technologies along with a growing awareness of the advantages of leds   led lighting offers some key advantages when compared to the oldfashioned incandescent light bulb invented by thomas edison reduced energy use reduced heat generation increased life expectancy lightemitting diodes supply a lowenergy source of lighting led fixtures used for lighting as opposed to those used to create a glowing effect on signs and equipment include numerous leds that together create white light that illuminates an area effectively  led lights hold a number of advantages in comparison to compact fluorescent light bulbs or cfls the coiled bulbs that have replaced many traditional incandescent light bulbs   the energysaving capacity of led lights means they’re better for the environment than traditional forms of lighting keep energy bills lower leds last for a long time typically far longer than fluorescent bulbs furthermore leds are durable not breaking as easily as bulbs the ability of leds to direct light in a specific direction is one of their primary benefits while cfls emit light in all directions  cfl bulbs often fall short of their expected lifespans led lights typically come with at least threeyear warranties according to the epa   use our energy saving led tubes as a retrofit or new installation led lights can be easily installed just like conventional lighting as an example led t’s fit existing sockets with just a slight wiring modification led fluorescent light replacements offer bright light low heat with the cost saving and many have a feature of no ballast required   a wide variety of leds including t tubes and edison base screw in bulbs are available contact our office for specific pricing   ft w ° t tubes ft w ° t tubes description specifications product description easily replaces a fluorescent t tube in appearance use existing fixtures with simple wiring external driver provides immediate start up excellent replacement for refrigerated case lighting lifespan is  hours  year factory warranty t  degree led tube power consumption  watt lumens average of  per watt end cap bipin beam angle  degrees kelvin   and  input power ac  to v power factor above  cri  replacement value  watt fluorescent tube and ballast warranty  hours   years certifications ul ce rohs   a led bulb a led bulb description specifications product description unique double layers with patented structure design ensure both safety and performance low voltage solution can be matched with various equipment such as solar emergency and portable lighting dimmable and non dimmable available   a model number qpae working voltage  vac dimmable voltage  vac available bases e e kelvin k k k power consumption watt watt watt efficacy lmw lmw lmw dimensions mm x mm cri above  warranty  hours certifications ul ce rohs patent  zl     br led lamp br led lamp specifications br  edison base dimmable power consumption  watts lumens average of  per watt base medium edison beam angle  kelvin    input power  volt power factor above  cri  replacement value  watt halogen warranty  hours certifications ul ce rohs energy star pse   par  dimmable par  dimmable description specifications product description consumes only w to replace w halogen or incandescent lighting f