part please have your order number ready upon calling acent will issue a returned materials authorization number rma shipping is nonrefundable a restocking fee up to  may be applied to all returned items any returned parts issued cod or freight collect will be refused cancellations  to cancel an order you must contact customer support at  as soon as possible orders that have shipped cannot be canceled and will have to follow the returned parts policy refunds  refunds on returned parts or canceled orders will be issued minus applicable fees eg restocking within  business days minimum order  we have a  minimum order to help cover costs this does not include freight payments  all payments must be made in full at time of order we accept visa master card and discover  all prices are subject to change without notice please call for the most current price sales tax  our company has offices in the state of nevada from a sales tax perspective a permanent physical presence in a state establishes a condition known as “nexus” we are required to collect sales tax in the region where the company has nexus about us acent technologies inc  n rainbow rd   las vegas nv    fax contact us july  m t w t f s s « feb              designed by the computer guys  powered by wordpress company info  acent technologies home led lights grow lights night blinds product graphics gaskets strip curtains leasing utility rebates contact us about us return policy navigation menu home » company info acent tech going green our featured products are “simple green solutions” for saving energy in grocery and convenience stores and all kinds of businesses learn more meta log in entries rss comments rss wordpressorg about us acent technologies inc  n rainbow rd   las vegas nv    fax contact us july  m t w t f s s « feb              designed by the computer guys  powered by wordpress about us  acent technologies home led lights grow lights night blinds product graphics gaskets strip curtains leasing utility re